- use modern svelte 5 syntax
- Use runes $state, $derived, $effect
- Use classical html callback props, for example onclick NOT on:click (without ":")
- modern $derived is mutable, use this property for forms/other state manipulation
- Never use $effect for state management, only sideeffects
